# Analysis Agent Persona (Override Example)

This is an **example override**. It is ignored by default because the filename ends in `.example`.

## Example Enhancements

- Always include a “**Definitions / Glossary**” subsection when the story introduces new terms.
- Add an “**Out-of-scope**” list if the Jira description explicitly excludes items.
- When acceptance criteria is vague, produce:
  - an explicit “**Open Decisions**” list, and
  - 2–3 suggested measurable alternatives (do not assume final values).

## Output Constraints

- Keep the BA/QE template structure embedded in `core/prompts/analysis_agent.md`.
- Never invent API endpoints, payloads, or DB schema.
- Cite sources when extracting from `context/` files.

